Even then , she was far too well bred to gratify her curiosity with any impatience . 
For a moment , they were riveted . 
Next she had plucked her gaze home again like a tame bird who should have meditated flight . 
I wonder , will I have met my fate ? she thought , and her heart swelled . 
Though he had never before set eyes on him , Archie had no difficulty in identifying him , and no hesitation in pronouncing him vulgar , the worst of the family . 
